; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 656-661
; Tests the balance assertion error when a transaction doesn't balance.
; When real postings don't sum to zero and there's no null posting,
; finalize() throws a balance error.

2024/03/01 Unbalanced
    Expenses:Food     $10.00
    Assets:Cash       $-5.00

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 8:
While balancing transaction from "$FILE", lines 6-8:
> 2024/03/01 Unbalanced
>     Expenses:Food     $10.00
>     Assets:Cash       $-5.00
Unbalanced remainder is:
               $5.00
Amount to balance against:
              $10.00
Error: Transaction does not balance
end test
